1
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:26,030
[The Princess Royal]

2
00:01:26,030 --> 00:01:28,950
[Adapted from Mo Shu Bai's novel,
The Princess Royal on jjwxc.net]

3
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:30,020
[This is a work of fiction.]

4
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
[Episode 31]

5
00:01:33,300 --> 00:01:36,260
I've always wanted to suppress
the northern enemies

6
00:01:36,900 --> 00:01:38,940
to keep our country safe
from constant skirmishes.

7
00:01:41,300 --> 00:01:41,980
Official Pei,

8
00:01:42,380 --> 00:01:43,660
do you have any useful suggestions?

9
00:01:45,100 --> 00:01:45,900
Perhaps

10
00:01:46,500 --> 00:01:48,260
we could hold
a military examination next year.

11
00:01:48,660 --> 00:01:49,460
A military examination?

12
00:01:51,540 --> 00:01:52,540
That's a brilliant idea.

13
00:01:54,740 --> 00:01:56,020
I have always wanted to build

14
00:01:56,020 --> 00:01:57,820
an army that truly belongs
to the royal family.

15
00:01:58,420 --> 00:01:59,380
It's a good idea
to hold a military examination.

16
00:02:03,260 --> 00:02:05,820
After we suppress the northern enemies,

17
00:02:06,620 --> 00:02:09,020
I plan to station an army
of 100,000 men in the South

18
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:10,300
permanently

19
00:02:10,820 --> 00:02:12,420
to spread our culture

20
00:02:12,540 --> 00:02:13,700
and influence foreign enemies

21
00:02:13,900 --> 00:02:14,860
so that 100 years from now,

22
00:02:15,380 --> 00:02:17,500
the southern lands
will be unified as one.

23
00:02:19,220 --> 00:02:20,580
Your Majesty, your exceptional foresight

24
00:02:20,780 --> 00:02:22,140
will make your plans
come to fruition eventually.

25
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:23,580
Besides,

26
00:02:24,300 --> 00:02:25,820
the southern lands have been
plagued by floods for years.

27
00:02:26,500 --> 00:02:29,060
Instead of repairing the dam
all the time,

28
00:02:29,500 --> 00:02:31,460
we should build another channel
to divert the water flow.

29
00:02:33,300 --> 00:02:34,100
Unfortunately,

30
00:02:34,860 --> 00:02:36,990
the elite troops, money, and food
in the country

31
00:02:36,990 --> 00:02:38,460
all belong to the noble families.

32
00:02:40,420 --> 00:02:41,340
But the noble families

33
00:02:42,900 --> 00:02:44,060
only care for their self-preservation.

34
00:02:45,060 --> 00:02:46,980
Let alone start wars at the borders,

35
00:02:47,540 --> 00:02:49,060
even if there is a war in the capital,

36
00:02:49,420 --> 00:02:50,980
they will only try to negotiate
rather than fight.

37
00:02:52,380 --> 00:02:53,540
Those cowards.

38
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:03,180
What do you think of what I said?

39
00:03:05,460 --> 00:03:06,620
You are a wise emperor.

40
00:03:06,980 --> 00:03:08,500
I dare not say anything otherwise.

41
00:03:09,140 --> 00:03:10,140
Just speak your mind.

42
00:03:13,700 --> 00:03:15,780
My clan came from a humble background.

43
00:03:16,140 --> 00:03:18,060
We gained our reputation
for your appreciation.

44
00:03:18,620 --> 00:03:20,340
My father has always been
your loyal supporter

45
00:03:20,980 --> 00:03:23,300
and I will follow in his footsteps.

46
00:03:25,540 --> 00:03:26,300
Very well.

47
00:03:28,380 --> 00:03:31,460
Your family
and Cheng's mother's kinsfolk

48
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:33,580
may have been commoners,

49
00:03:34,380 --> 00:03:35,460
unlike those from the noble families,

50
00:03:36,140 --> 00:03:39,420
but you have a heart of gold.

51
00:03:39,940 --> 00:03:44,180
In the future, I hope you'll continue
assisting me in the state affairs.

52
00:03:47,380 --> 00:03:48,380
Especially Cheng.

53
00:03:48,780 --> 00:03:49,780
He's still young.

54
00:03:51,340 --> 00:03:53,980
You should guide him on his journey

55
00:03:54,180 --> 00:03:55,140
on my behalf to share my burdens,

56
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:56,300
understood?

57
00:03:58,660 --> 00:03:59,580
I understand.

58
00:04:03,260 --> 00:04:03,980
Mr. Pei.

59
00:04:06,260 --> 00:04:07,940
His Majesty has high expectations for you.

60
00:04:10,620 --> 00:04:13,140
Has His Majesty been
experiencing health issues lately?

61
00:04:19,540 --> 00:04:21,300
His Majesty has been experiencing

62
00:04:21,420 --> 00:04:23,460
temporary blindness in the morning
for the past two days.

63
00:04:24,060 --> 00:04:26,020
We are secretly searching
for famous physicians.

64
00:04:29,860 --> 00:04:30,460
Mr. Pei,

65
00:04:31,300 --> 00:04:32,900
you have to plan ahead.

66
00:04:33,940 --> 00:04:35,460
His Majesty wanted me to remind you

67
00:04:36,140 --> 00:04:37,700
that only the commoners
will truly support you.

68
00:04:40,980 --> 00:04:43,260
I have conveyed His Majesty's message.

69
00:04:43,580 --> 00:04:44,540
I'll take my leave.

70
00:04:52,620 --> 00:04:54,180
Looks like chaos is drawing near.

71
00:05:00,820 --> 00:05:02,860
Mr. Pei, Consort Rou
wants to see you now.

72
00:05:13,820 --> 00:05:14,620
Mr. Pei, a moment, please.

73
00:05:18,740 --> 00:05:19,380
Your Highness.

74
00:05:20,420 --> 00:05:22,380
Mr. Pei, come in, please.

75
00:05:27,620 --> 00:05:30,180
Greetings, Your Highnesses.

76
00:05:33,020 --> 00:05:35,620
This time, we've got ourselves
into huge trouble

77
00:05:35,940 --> 00:05:37,580
for taking down Wang Houwen.

78
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:44,060
I have something to tell you.

79
00:05:44,740 --> 00:05:46,300
Privately, if possible.

80
00:05:48,620 --> 00:05:50,420
All of you may leave now.

81
00:05:52,940 --> 00:05:53,940
I'll take my leave.

82
00:06:03,860 --> 00:06:06,060
It's a fact that no one would dare
to offend the noble families.

83
00:06:06,620 --> 00:06:07,380
However,

84
00:06:08,180 --> 00:06:09,620
we can't simply do nothing.

85
00:06:10,260 --> 00:06:11,620
After all, His Majesty is watching.

86
00:06:13,940 --> 00:06:15,180
Now that Wang Houwen
has been gotten rid of,

87
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:16,860
you have taken your stand.

88
00:06:17,340 --> 00:06:18,780
When you release the others afterward,

89
00:06:19,460 --> 00:06:20,580
the noble families would think

90
00:06:21,020 --> 00:06:22,540
that you're doing them a favor.

91
00:06:24,580 --> 00:06:27,380
If you release them from the beginning,

92
00:06:27,900 --> 00:06:29,380
would the noble families still think

93
00:06:29,660 --> 00:06:32,420
that you're showing them grace?

94
00:06:35,060 --> 00:06:36,180
Besides, this is the only way

95
00:06:36,900 --> 00:06:37,660
to create

96
00:06:37,900 --> 00:06:40,340
an opportunity for Prince Su
to recruit talents.

97
00:06:42,220 --> 00:06:43,780
Had I not done all that,

98
00:06:43,940 --> 00:06:46,340
the noble families might have assumed
that you're scared of them.

99
00:06:47,580 --> 00:06:50,300
You spoke my mind.

100
00:06:54,980 --> 00:06:56,140
Mr. Pei,

101
00:06:56,300 --> 00:06:57,940
as the chief examiner
for the metropolitan examination,

102
00:06:58,100 --> 00:06:59,860
I'm sure it won't be hard for you

103
00:07:00,100 --> 00:07:02,100
to put a few names
on the primary list of candidates.

104
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,420
[Yang Xu, Wang Zhao, Wen Tong,
Tian Xiwen, Liu Li, Chen Qing]

105
00:07:07,980 --> 00:07:09,740
Aren't these people
all from noble families?

106
00:07:10,260 --> 00:07:12,380
Why don't they just follow
the Royal Selection route?

107
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:14,260
Their names are not included
in the noble families' pedigrees.

108
00:07:14,940 --> 00:07:16,860
They're only related to them somehow.

109
00:07:24,940 --> 00:07:25,620
Your Highness,

110
00:07:26,180 --> 00:07:29,180
there are some things
that I'm not sure if I should say.

111
00:07:29,300 --> 00:07:30,460
Pray tell.

112
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:38,220
What do you want, Your Highness?
It's getting a large amount of money

113
00:07:38,300 --> 00:07:40,300
and live a peaceful life in the palace,

114
00:07:40,820 --> 00:07:41,700
or

115
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:44,060
making Prince Su

116
00:07:45,780 --> 00:07:47,020
ascend the throne?

117
00:07:52,380 --> 00:07:53,620
Sorry for my abruptness.

118
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:57,140
But there are limited positions

119
00:07:57,180 --> 00:07:58,620
in the imperial court.

120
00:07:58,780 --> 00:07:59,980
Having more people
from the noble families

121
00:08:00,260 --> 00:08:02,220
means there will be fewer opportunities
for real commoners.

122
00:08:02,540 --> 00:08:05,460
You should know better than I do

123
00:08:05,940 --> 00:08:07,460
who can be of value to Prince Su.

124
00:08:11,980 --> 00:08:13,180
The metropolitan examination
will commence

125
00:08:13,300 --> 00:08:14,600
[Notice of Metropolitan Examination]
on the 10th day of the 10th month

126
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,860
in the 25th year of the Yongning Era.

127
00:08:15,980 --> 00:08:18,500
There will be two categories
of passing candidates.

128
00:08:18,820 --> 00:08:21,460
Those on the Primary List will be
appointed directly in the capital

129
00:08:21,860 --> 00:08:24,140
and those on the Secondary List will be
appointed in regional governments.

130
00:08:25,020 --> 00:08:26,260
That doesn't sound very appealing.

131
00:08:26,380 --> 00:08:27,780
I heard those regional positions
are posts with very little to do.

132
00:08:28,300 --> 00:08:30,500
We'd better study harder.

133
00:08:30,740 --> 00:08:33,660
After all, those on the Primary List
can work directly in the capital.

134
00:08:33,900 --> 00:08:35,300
That depends on whether we can pass.

135
00:08:35,900 --> 00:08:36,700
Yeah.

136
00:08:36,700 --> 00:08:42,820
[Examination Hall]

137
00:09:15,140 --> 00:09:16,100
Your Majesty,

138
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:18,780
these are the candidates
for the palace examination.

139
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:23,420
- Greetings, Your Majesty.
- Greetings, Your Majesty.

140
00:09:23,580 --> 00:09:26,740
- Long live Your Majesty!
- Long live Your Majesty!

141
00:09:26,900 --> 00:09:29,300
You may rise.

142
00:09:29,420 --> 00:09:30,700
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thank you, Your Majesty.

143
00:09:31,180 --> 00:09:33,780
Please set a question
for the candidates, Your Majesty.

144
00:09:35,060 --> 00:09:36,820
How can a ruler ensure
that his officials

145
00:09:37,860 --> 00:09:39,300
are free from corruption,
that his people harbor no greed,

146
00:09:39,740 --> 00:09:40,940
and that every family
can sustain themselves?

147
00:09:41,620 --> 00:09:43,220
How can the ruler maintain the country's
traditions and culture,

148
00:09:43,780 --> 00:09:44,980
create an education system
that is accessible to all,

149
00:09:45,340 --> 00:09:46,620
and build a competitive
agricultural industry?

150
00:09:46,900 --> 00:09:48,580
A good strategist knows
how to win a battle without fighting.

151
00:09:48,780 --> 00:09:50,660
A good general knows
how to quash his enemy's plans

152
00:09:50,820 --> 00:09:52,180
to end a battle

153
00:09:52,300 --> 00:09:54,540
even before it starts.

154
00:09:55,260 --> 00:09:56,300
Discuss the topics above.

155
00:09:57,300 --> 00:09:58,700
I shall read your answers myself.

156
00:09:59,660 --> 00:10:01,060
Out of the seven major noble families
in the capital,

157
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:03,420
other than the four main ones
who have lasted for nine generations,

158
00:10:03,780 --> 00:10:05,780
I see we have representatives
from the other three noble families.

159
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:08,300
I'm greatly honored
by your gracious presence.

160
00:10:10,420 --> 00:10:13,540
Your Highness, we're here
to congratulate you in advance

161
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:16,180
for taking back the Inspectorate Office
from Consort Rou

162
00:10:16,420 --> 00:10:18,260
and being reinstated as the Supervisor
of the Inspectorate Office.

163
00:10:19,300 --> 00:10:20,540
You jest, Mr. Wang.

164
00:10:21,300 --> 00:10:22,060
The Inspectorate Office

165
00:10:22,060 --> 00:10:24,260
is doing fine under the leadership
of Consort Rou and Prince Su.

166
00:10:24,420 --> 00:10:25,780
What do I have to do with this?

167
00:10:28,300 --> 00:10:29,540
We're here today

168
00:10:29,820 --> 00:10:31,540
to discuss with you

169
00:10:31,940 --> 00:10:34,580
how we can help you

170
00:10:34,780 --> 00:10:37,540
regain the Inspectorate Office's
leadership.

171
00:11:01,420 --> 00:11:03,540
Your Highness, if you have any request,

172
00:11:04,060 --> 00:11:05,140
pray tell.

173
00:11:10,260 --> 00:11:11,700
Mr. Zheng, you're a sensible one.

174
00:11:14,660 --> 00:11:16,940
Actually, I know why exactly

175
00:11:16,940 --> 00:11:18,060
you're here today.

176
00:11:18,820 --> 00:11:19,900
Instead of putting it as helping me,

177
00:11:19,900 --> 00:11:22,420
I'd say that you're helping yourselves.

178
00:11:24,940 --> 00:11:26,540
The fall season is ending soon.

179
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:28,700
The officials that Consort Rou
has dealt with

180
00:11:28,700 --> 00:11:30,780
will all be executed by then.

181
00:11:30,940 --> 00:11:33,660
You want me to take over
and change the original sentence

182
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:35,580
so that your family members
won't be executed,

183
00:11:36,420 --> 00:11:37,540
especially Mr. Wang's.

184
00:11:41,300 --> 00:11:43,060
Let me guess what's on your mind.

185
00:11:43,180 --> 00:11:46,180
Consort Rou is ambitious and bears
a grudge against the noble families.

186
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:47,660
If no one stops her,

187
00:11:47,660 --> 00:11:48,580
she will become

188
00:11:48,900 --> 00:11:50,500
a threat in the long term.

189
00:11:51,940 --> 00:11:54,020
While she's reforming the system
of the imperial examination today,

190
00:11:54,020 --> 00:11:57,140
in the future, she might be targeting

191
00:11:57,300 --> 00:11:59,300
your military forces, power,
and supplies.

192
00:12:01,260 --> 00:12:02,500
You see everything clearly,
Your Highness.

193
00:12:04,500 --> 00:12:05,660
Right now,

194
00:12:05,820 --> 00:12:07,500
Consort Rou
is under my father's protection,

195
00:12:08,020 --> 00:12:09,500
so if you take action
against Consort Rou,

196
00:12:10,060 --> 00:12:11,540
you would be taking action
against my father.

197
00:12:11,660 --> 00:12:13,940
Yet, you wouldn't want to confront
my father directly,

198
00:12:14,020 --> 00:12:15,500
so you're trying to make me

199
00:12:15,660 --> 00:12:16,900
a puppet of yours

200
00:12:17,180 --> 00:12:19,900
and manipulate me
to start a war against my father.

201
00:12:24,060 --> 00:12:25,060
However,

202
00:12:25,900 --> 00:12:27,620
why would I want

203
00:12:28,660 --> 00:12:30,340
to become someone's puppet?

204
00:12:33,500 --> 00:12:34,580
You've misunderstood us, Your Highness.

205
00:12:34,860 --> 00:12:37,220
We're here to assist you,

206
00:12:37,420 --> 00:12:39,660
not to manipulate you.

207
00:12:46,460 --> 00:12:47,820
So, you're willing to follow my orders?

208
00:12:55,220 --> 00:12:56,620
Inform the Prince Consort

209
00:12:57,100 --> 00:12:59,180
that I will ask Chen Houzhao
to enter the capital tonight

210
00:12:59,340 --> 00:13:00,660
to lodge a case
at the Ministry of Justice.

211
00:13:00,780 --> 00:13:02,340
Tell him to order Pei Liming to act.

212
00:13:02,380 --> 00:13:03,860
Make sure Su Rongqing doesn't intercept.

213
00:13:04,660 --> 00:13:05,460
Also,

214
00:13:05,980 --> 00:13:07,140
prepare the testimonies provided

215
00:13:07,220 --> 00:13:09,300
by the candidates which shows
that they were coerced by Consort Rou

216
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:10,300
to drop their cases.

217
00:13:10,300 --> 00:13:11,260
I want to read them tonight.

218
00:13:11,940 --> 00:13:13,420
You also need to inform Miss Shangguan

219
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:16,020
to prepare the evidence

220
00:13:16,180 --> 00:13:17,220
showing they used torture
to force a confession.

221
00:13:20,180 --> 00:13:21,740
Also, prepare a nice set
of clothes for me.

222
00:13:22,380 --> 00:13:23,180
Tomorrow,

223
00:13:23,780 --> 00:13:25,020
I must look pretty
when I attend the morning audience.

224
00:13:25,300 --> 00:13:25,980
Understood.

225
00:13:33,140 --> 00:13:33,940
[Taiji Hall]
Your Majesty,

226
00:13:34,460 --> 00:13:37,020
Wang Houwen and his accomplices
should be executed according to the law.

227
00:13:37,460 --> 00:13:40,140
Please decide on a date
for their execution.

228
00:13:41,460 --> 00:13:42,620
I hope you can reconsider
your decision, Your Majesty.

229
00:13:42,620 --> 00:13:44,180
My father was the Minister of Personnel.

230
00:13:44,500 --> 00:13:47,060
We have only listened
to Consort Rou's side of the story.

231
00:13:47,540 --> 00:13:48,500
That's not enough to prove his guilt.

232
00:13:49,140 --> 00:13:51,620
Therefore, I implore you
to postpone the execution.

233
00:13:51,860 --> 00:13:54,380
The execution dates have always been set
by the Bureau of Astronomy.

234
00:13:54,620 --> 00:13:56,540
Since when is this
a topic of discussion in the court?

235
00:13:56,820 --> 00:13:58,140
You've been working here for years.

236
00:13:58,300 --> 00:13:59,900
Don't you know the rules?

237
00:14:00,060 --> 00:14:01,860
You have a point, Mr. Shangguan.

238
00:14:02,060 --> 00:14:05,380
A woman usurps a man's power,
which will destabilize the country.

239
00:14:08,140 --> 00:14:09,540
What are you implying, Mr. Gu?

240
00:14:11,260 --> 00:14:11,940
Your Highness.

241
00:14:12,820 --> 00:14:15,340
I am just fulfilling my duties
as a censor.

242
00:14:16,300 --> 00:14:17,940
You're calling me
a woman usurping a man's power.

243
00:14:18,340 --> 00:14:20,220
Why didn't you say the same thing

244
00:14:20,220 --> 00:14:21,300
when Princess Pingyue was here?

245
00:14:21,580 --> 00:14:23,020
At least, Rong didn't make

246
00:14:23,020 --> 00:14:24,500
that many wrongful convictions.

247
00:14:25,140 --> 00:14:26,580
Why are the officials
unsatisfied with you?

248
00:14:27,020 --> 00:14:29,220
Consort Rou, shouldn't you
do some self-reflection?

249
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:31,940
You're all ganging up against me!

250
00:14:40,140 --> 00:14:41,180
Your Highness,

251
00:14:41,460 --> 00:14:43,100
you said that I've made
wrongful convictions.

252
00:14:43,540 --> 00:14:44,460
Do you have any evidence?

253
00:14:46,660 --> 00:14:47,900
If not,

254
00:14:48,260 --> 00:14:48,860
then you...

255
00:14:48,860 --> 00:14:49,540
I do.

256
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:07,220
Greetings, Father.

257
00:15:07,460 --> 00:15:10,380
Long live Your Majesty.

258
00:15:10,700 --> 00:15:11,740
I didn't summon you.

259
00:15:12,580 --> 00:15:13,780
What are you doing here?

260
00:15:14,020 --> 00:15:15,260
For myself,

261
00:15:15,660 --> 00:15:16,580
for officials,

262
00:15:16,940 --> 00:15:18,620
and for all scholars of humble roots,

263
00:15:18,980 --> 00:15:22,100
I'd like to seek justice
from Consort Xiao Rou.

264
00:15:22,700 --> 00:15:25,140
I hope you can give us justice, Father.

