as a cowardly emperor,

608
00:35:46,660 --> 00:35:48,820
and the Shangguan Family could
ensure you're well taken care of.

609
00:35:48,900 --> 00:35:51,220
Yet, you are unwilling to do so.

610
00:35:54,060 --> 00:35:56,820
