614
00:36:11,700 --> 00:36:13,660
Wait till you reach the end...

615
00:36:15,300 --> 00:36:18,540
and die alone.

616
00:36:53,100 --> 00:36:53,780
Your Majesty.

617
00:36:54,980 --> 00:36:57,540
Consort Rou has been sent to prison.

618
00:36:59,100 --> 00:37:00,500
