Fulai.

620
00:37:09,340 --> 00:37:10,140
Yes, Your Majesty.

621
00:37:11,060 --> 00:37:13,460
I remember that when I first met you...

622
00:37:15,780 --> 00:37:17,500
you were only 11 years old, right?

623
00:37:19,140 --> 00:37:19,940
Your Majesty,

624
00:37:21,060 --> 00:37:23,380
I had just turned 11 back then.

625
00:37:29,620 --> 00:37:30,420
Have we...

626
00:37:32,660 --> 00:37:34,620
all grown old?

627
00:37:34,820 --> 00:37:35,540
Your Majesty.

628
00:37:36,780 --> 00:37:41,420
I have been serving you
for almost 40 years.

629
00:37:48,740 --> 00:37:50,580
Ever since I was ten years old,

630
00:37:52,660 --> 00:37:55,220
I swore I would be a good emperor.

631
00:37:59,060 --> 00:38:01,460
I worked diligently for decades,

632
00:38:03,580 --> 00:38:04,380
but now...

633
00:38:07,100 --> 00:38:09,460
