to be back to square one.

634
00:38:11,660 --> 00:38:13,060
I am all alone.

635
00:38:17,740 --> 00:38:19,220
I finally understand

636
00:38:20,780 --> 00:38:22,220
why people

637
00:38:24,940 --> 00:38:27,900
