Yes, Your Majesty.

645
00:39:32,020 --> 00:39:33,420
Consort Rou has fallen.

646
00:39:34,420 --> 00:39:36,500
It's time to clean house.

647
00:39:54,180 --> 00:39:54,900
Mother!

648
00:39:55,940 --> 00:39:56,660
Huayue.

649
00:39:57,700 --> 00:39:58,700
Why are you here?

650
