671
00:40:53,380 --> 00:40:55,060
Stop thinking about how you can save me.

672
00:40:55,940 --> 00:40:58,700
I'm afraid I can't escape death
this time.

673
00:41:01,300 --> 00:41:02,780
What you should do now

674
00:41:03,060 --> 00:41:05,980
