in prison anymore.

679
00:41:20,900 --> 00:41:22,420
Sever all ties with me.

680
00:41:22,620 --> 00:41:23,980
Beg your father

681
00:41:25,260 --> 00:41:29,300
to allow you and Cheng to move to stay
with your uncle,

682
00:41:30,940 --> 00:41:32,300
stay away from the royal family,

683
00:41:32,940 --> 00:41:35,180
and lead a peaceful life.

684
00:41:35,420 --> 00:41:36,740
No, I don't want this path.

685
00:41:38,380 --> 00:41:39,460
The second path is...

686
00:41:41,980 --> 00:41:44,300
You need to take a gamble
and risk everything you have.

687
00:41:44,300 --> 00:41:45,860
It will be very difficult, though.

688
00:41:45,860 --> 00:41:47,780
Mother, just tell me what to do.

689
00:41:48,740 --> 00:41:50,180
Kill Li Chuan.

690
00:41:52,540 --> 00:41:53,340
Better yet,

691
00:41:54,620 --> 00:41:56,980
