699
00:42:26,980 --> 00:42:27,700
Huayue.

700
00:42:29,820 --> 00:42:32,900
No matter which path you choose,

701
00:42:34,780 --> 00:42:36,940
I will write a confession

702
00:42:38,060 --> 00:42:40,460
to take all the blame

703
00:42:40,980 --> 00:42:45,020
so that you and Cheng will remain safe.

704
00:42:47,180 --> 00:42:48,020
Huayue.

